### 1. Valid expense under $100 -> Auto-approved
POST http://localhost:7071/api/expenses/start
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "employee_name": "Josue Muhire",
  "employee_email": "josue@example.com",
  "amount": 75,
  "category": "travel",
  "description": "Taxi from airport to client site",
  "manager_email": "manager@example.com"
}

### 2. Valid expense >= $100 -> Manager approves
POST http://localhost:7071/api/expenses/start
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "employee_name": "Josue Muhire",
  "employee_email": "josue@example.com",
  "amount": 250,
  "category": "software",
  "description": "Annual software subscription",
  "manager_email": "manager@example.com"
}

### Check approved expense status
GET http://localhost:7071/api/expenses/status/e2d7d3e5c91f41e5bc1b22f4b852c228